# Tangent Forge Website Project

## Overview
A modern, readable website for Tangent Forge - turning creative tangents into shippable products. Built for freelance writers and creators.

## Tech Stack
- Static HTML/CSS/JS
- Netlify hosting & forms
- Inter font, CSS custom properties
- Mobile-first responsive design

## Key Files
- `tangentforge-site/index.html` - Main page
- `tangentforge-site/style.css` - All styling
- `tangentforge-site/tokens.css` - Design system variables
- `tangentforge-site/script.js` - Interactive features
- `netlify.toml` - Deployment config
- `dev_files/` - Enhanced version with documentation

## Current Status
- ✅ Deployed to Netlify
- ✅ Connected to GitHub auto-deploy
- ✅ Email form working
- ⏳ Need Gumroad product link
- ⏳ Need to create actual 30-prompt pack

## Design Principles
- Maximum readability (17px base font, high contrast)
- Clean, professional appearance
- Fast loading (<20KB total)
- Mobile-first responsive

